Package entity.user

Class Applicant

java.lang.Object
entity.user.User
entity.user.Applicant
Direct Known Subclasses:
Officer
public class Applicant extends User
Applicant class definition in the BTO system. The applicant can apply for BTO projects, view their application status, and manage enquiries related to their application.
